#### Summary
&nbsp;
In the 9th year protocol work group call, participants reviewed NEP 536 and NEP 540. NEP 536, presented by Evgeny Kuzyakov, proposed adjustments to gas refunds, with all four working group members leaning towards approval.

However, NEP 540, addressing storage staking adjustments, faced rejection, with all members opposing the proposal due to concerns about its potential risks and limitations. 

Despite differing voting outcomes, the group engaged in constructive discussions about alternative solutions and emphasized the importance of balancing protocol efficiency and developer experience. 

The call concluded with an emphasis on community involvement and resources for NEAR developers.
&nbsp;
**Approved:** NEP-536
**Rejected:** NEP-540

