protocol-work-group-call-8-3272:
**Moderator:** @victorkanu1.near
&nbsp;
#### Summary
&nbsp;
The NEAR Protocol Work Group voted on NEP-519 (Support for yielded execution.)

With all voting indications leaning towards approval, NEP-519 was approved by the Work Group, This proposal introduces the capability for smart contracts in the NEAR protocol to delay responding to callers until observing future transactions, addressing situations where immediate responses are not feasible.

A big thank you was extended to the author for submitting this NEP and to everyone who helped review them. 
The recording will be posted on our YouTube https://youtube.com/@NEARDevHub/videos
